type script : 
youtube : 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ECR36qoVXvY&list=PLTEzTFAAzxQ6yvftZpvM2LJCv6b4zYVhJ


install : 
1- npm i -g typescript
2- tsc -v

run :
1- tsc namefile.ts

Configuring the TypeScript Compiler
1- tsc --init


موارد مهم Configuring :
1- target : 
2- module : 
3- "rootDir": "./src",
4- "outDir": "./dist",
5- removeComments : true
6- noEmitOnError: true

Debugging:
"sourceMap": true,

file Launch.json =>      
    "preLaunchTask": "tsc: build - tsconfig.json",

